name: Dntel
description: '''James Scott Tamborello''', (born 1975) also known by his stage name '''Dntel''' {{IPAc-en|ˈ|d|ɪ|n|t|ɛ|l}}, is an American [[electronic music]] artist and [[DJ]]. Aside from his main solo project, Tamborello is also known as a member of the groups [[The Postal Service]], [[#Other projects|Headset]], [[Strictly Ballroom (band)|Strictly Ballroom]], and [[Figurine (band)|Figurine]], where he is sometimes cited as '''James Figurine'''.
